{"tid":201450,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"輕/漫改既原作內容同動畫好看與否係二回事","createTime":"2017-04-14T17:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T19:54:46.000Z","uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49c08e074fbc38343ff24c12982e72009ae7b88a","tid":201450,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"2年前榎宫祐靠ngnl一戰成名 今季有另一套作品時鍾機關<br />\n<br />\n追完小說無論係劇情鋪排 內容 都係ngnl拎左唔少經驗過去<br />\n<br />\n但係動畫化之後連討論都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一季既熱情傳奇 普通王道漫內容 但只要係ufo做<br />\n<br />\n就大把人爭住j作畫<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得 無論係幾好 幾爛既內容都只係視乎製作組有冇心幫你做<br />\n<br />\n好似極黑的....東京食屍 有一定內容支撐 都可以比人搞到爛一爛<br />\n<br />\n新妹dxd只要畫得夠大波都可以稱為佳作<br />\n<br />\n我肯定被稱為神作既無職 只要唔夠經費 都只會係垃圾<br />\n<br />\nfate唔係ufo做 都唔會玩到10年<br />\n<br />\n所以結論係 動畫同原作內容 我強烈建議將佢視為兩套作品黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6da1b9702eb2c56d16dad074ac6f824b32ec39","tid":201450,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:04:53.000Z","msg":"Fate啲畫面幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8043d815dc276dbd2d44f3780b765aab3920dcd","tid":201450,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"Fate 06年版係deen整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來自新世界垃圾作畫一樣大把人吹奏"},{"pid":"c6ed5f19a7060c0e5caaaffd72567e7240373471","tid":201450,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:08:41.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n所以要評一套野一定睇原作"},{"pid":"c072e5970a20731063f789e0a39300bd36cbcf65","tid":201450,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:12:37.000Z","msg":"game改"},{"pid":"7c646e21715f3d48c2418debf796b88fc545aa9b","tid":201450,"uid":39871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Fate 06年版係deen整<img src=\"/ass